        <p>Use this method to quickly insert the first word located after your cursor as an index keyword.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Advantage </span>It is extremely fast.</li>
            <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Disadvantage </span>It is not the method to use if you want to customize your phrase, use a variable, or add a second-level keyword. The word located immediately after the cursor is exactly what will be displayed in the index. </li>
